{"word":"G2151 - εὐσεβέω - eusebéō - yoo-seb-eh'-o - Show piety","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐσεβέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eusebéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-seb-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Show piety</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆராதி, தேவபக்தியாய் விசாரி"},{"paragraph":"to act piously or reverently"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2152 - εὐσεβής - eusebḗs - yoo-seb-ace'/2152\">G2152</a>; to <i>be pious</i>, that is, (towards God) to <i>worship</i>, or (towards parents) to <i>respect</i> (<i>support</i>): - show piety, worship.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2150/2150\">G2150</a>, <a href=\"#/G2151/2151\">G2151</a>, <a href=\"#/G2152/2152\">G2152</a>, <a href=\"#/G2153/2153\">G2153</a>, <a href=\"#/G4573/4573\">G4573</a>, <a href=\"#/G4574/4574\">G4574</a>, <a href=\"#/G4575/4575\">G4575</a>, <a href=\"#/G4576/4576\">G4576</a>, <a href=\"#/G763/763\">G763</a>, <a href=\"#/G764/764\">G764</a>, <a href=\"#/G765/765\">G765</a>"}]}